./" This is the manpage of  burst"
.TH burst 8 "5-11-2016" "V1.0" "burst ManPage"

.SH NAME
burst

.SH DESCRIPTION
Command line utility that will take in a file and split it into line segments.

.SH Options
.IP -o
remove newline
.IP -csv
separates lines by , instead of newline
.IP -c
get html data from a website save into file and burst into smaller files
.IP -l
Returns the amount of lines in the file.
.IP -w
returns the amount of words in the file.

.SH SYNOPSIS
burst[file][size][commands][curlurl]
.SH AUTHOR
Mathew Wright 
